pension fork, and a proprietary belt drive:\r\n\r\n<img src="http://overvolted.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/carbonlab6.jpg" alt="carbonlab6" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-29" />\r\n\r\nFor you fanboys who can''t wait to get one of these toys to play with on the grounds of your new <a target="_blank" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dacha">dacha</a>, prices start at $7,000 plus shipping, but we have yet to hear how much the fur-lined, gold-plated version will cost.', 'Russian Aerospace Company Carbon Lab Shows Off New Carbon Fiber Ebike Prototypes', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '22-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-22 07:22:41', '2015-05-22 07:22:41', '', 22, 'http://overvolted.com/22-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
